# [Find Integer](http://acm.hdu.edu.cn/showproblem.php?pid=6441)
# 问题分析
题意：已知$a^n+b^n=c^n$，给出$n$和$a$，求$b$，$c$，如果无解输出$-1$。
**费马大定理**
1. $a^n+b^n=c^n$，$n>2$时无解。
2. 当$a$为奇数时，
<!--more-->
$a = 2 \cdot k + 1$

$c = k ^ 2 + (k + 1) ^ 2$

$b = c - 1$

当 $a$ 为偶数

$a = 2 * k + 2$

$c = 1 + (k + 1) ^ 2$

$b = c - 2$

# 代码

```c++
#include <bits/stdc++.h>

int main() {
    int T;
    scanf("%d", &T);
    while (T--) {
        int n, a;
        scanf("%d%d", &n, &a);
        if (n == 0 || n > 2) {
            printf("-1 -1\n");
        } else if (n == 1) {
            printf("%d %d\n", 1, a + 1);
        } else {
            long long b, c;
            if (a & 1) {
                int k = a / 2;
                c = k * 1LL * k + (k + 1) * 1LL * (k + 1);
                b = c - 1;
            } else {
                int k = (a - 2) / 2;
                c = 1 + 1LL * (k + 1) * (k + 1);
                b = c - 2;
            }
            if (b > 1e9 || c > 1e9)
                printf("-1 -1\n");
            else
                printf("%lld %lld\n", b, c);
        }
    }
}


```

